omplete. Part of 20,000+ product improvements across GitHub platform announced at February 2026 developer conference.\",\n    31→    \"updateType\": \"announcement\",\n    32→    \"url\": \"https://github.blog\",\n    33→    \"date\": \"2026-02-06\",\n    34→    \"community_feedback\": [\n    35→      {\n    36→        \"quote\": \"Basic configuration everyone should have - best completion/in-line coding at $10/month\",\n    37→        \"source\": \"2026年 AI 编程工具横评\",\n    38→        \"sentiment\": \"positive\"\n    39→      },\n    40→      {\n    41→        \"quote\": \"Emphasized expanding Copilot's capabilities beyond traditional code completion to more comprehensive AI-assisted development workflows\",\n    42→        \"source\": \"Industry commentary\",\n    43→        \"sentiment\": \"neutral\"\n    44→      }\n    45→    ]\n    46→  },\n    47→  {\n    48→    \"productName\": \"OpenAI Codex\",\n    49→    \"title\": \"macOS Application Release and GPT-5.3-Codex Model\",\n    50→    \"description\": \"OpenAI released macOS desktop application version of Codex in February 2026, featuring GPT-5.2-Codex model with 40% faster reasoning, 400k token input support, and 50+ programming languages. Integrated MCP protocol and 'work tree' mechanism for enhanced workflow management.\",\n    51→    \"updateType\": \"release\",\n    52→    \"url\": \"https://openai.com/codex\",\n    53→    \"date\": \"2026-02-09\",\n    54→    \"community_feedback\": [\n    55→      {\n    56→        \"quote\": \"OpenAI推出macOS版Codex应用并发布GPT-5.3编程模型\",\n    57→        \"source\": \"AI周报2.9 2026年2月第2周\",\n    58→        \"sentiment\": \"positive\"\n    59→      },\n    60→      {\n    61→        \"quote\": \"GPT-5-Codex连续干7小时'不累' - OpenAI最强编程模型\",\n    62→        \"source\": \"Tech media coverage\",\n    63→        \"sentiment\": \"positive\"\n    64→      }\n    65→    ]\n    66→  },\n    67→  {\n    68→    \"productName\": \"Gemini\",\n    69→    \"title\": \"Gemini 3 Pro Preview Deprecation Announcement\",\n    70→    \"description\": \"Google announced on February 26, 2026 that Gemini 3 Pro Preview would be officially deprecated in the Gemini API and AI Studio starting March 9, 2026. The '-latest' alias will automatically switch to Gemini 3.1 Pro Preview. Also announced multi-step task automation features during Samsung Galaxy S26 launch.\",\n    71→    \"updateType\": \"announcement\",\n    72→    \"url\": \"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs\",\n    73→    \"date\": \"2026-02-26\",\n    74→    \"community_feedback\": [\n    75→      {\n    76→        \"quote\": \"谷歌3月9日起停用Gemini 3 Pro Preview\",\n    77→        \"source\": \"Donews News\",\n    78→        \"sentiment\": \"neutral\"\n    79→      }\n    80→    ]\n    81→  },\n    82→  {\n    83→    \"productName\": \"AI Coding Tools Market\",\n    84→    \"title\": \"2026 AI Programming Tools Comprehensive Comparison\",\n    85→    \"description\": \"February 2026 saw extensive tool comparisons across Chinese tech communities. Market analysis identified Cursor, Claude Code, and Devin as 'three major engines' generating $3.1B+ in combined revenue. Windsurf's acquisition by Cognition AI (Devin's creators) and Claude model access restrictions affecting Windsurf were key market dynamics discussed.\",\n    86→    \"updateType\": \"announcement\",\n    87→    \"url\": \"https://juejin.cn/post/7605494530017280040\",\n    88→    \"date\": \"2026-02-11\",\n    89→    \"community_feedback\": [\n    90→      {\n    91→        \"quote\": \"2026年AI编程工具收入突破31亿美元，Cursor、Claude Code与Devin成三大引擎\",\n    92→        \"source\": \"Tencent News\",\n    93→        \"sentiment\": \"positive\"\n    94→      },\n    95→      {\n    96→        \"quote\": \"Windsurf被Cognition AI收购，Claude模型访问受限影响Windsurf用户\",\n    97→        \"source\": \"Chinese developer community\",\n    98→        \"sentiment\": \"negative\"\n    99→      },\n   100→      {\n   101→        \"quote\": \"Recommended stacks: Professional - Cursor/Windsurf